			<p>The recent completion of our acquisition of Tembec represents the opening of another new chapter for our company. Rayonier Advanced Materials is now a global manufacturer of high-purity cellulose, paperboard, lumber, and newsprint to high-yield pulp. If you are new to Rayonier Advanced Materials, we welcome you. If you are an existing customer or partner, you will appreciate our expanded product offerings, increased innovation and an even larger geographic footprint.</p>
